doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='About Ali Bińkowska - AI Training & HRTech Innovation')
        meta(name='author', content='Ali Bińkowska')

        title About Me - Ali Bińkowska

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
        include includes/css.pug

    body.d-flex.flex-column.h-100.bg-light
        main.flex-shrink-0
            include includes/navbar.pug

            // Page Header
            .container.px-5.my-5
                .text-center.mb-5
                    h1.display-5.fw-bolder.mb-0
                        span.text-gradient.d-inline About Me
                
                .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-11.col-xl-9.col-xxl-8
                        
                        // Philosophy Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                .mb-4
                                    h3.fw-bolder.mb-4 My Philosophy
                                    blockquote.blockquote.mb-4
                                        p.fst-italic.text-muted "I don't build to serve or to help anyone. I don't build to have clients. I have clients to build."
                                        footer.blockquote-footer.mt-2 Howard Roark, 
                                            cite The Fountainhead
                                    p This quote captures my approach perfectly. My purpose is to create the most valuable, best-constructed, and most impactful training and solutions possible. I strive to offer the best I have and teach others to recognize excellence in AI implementation.

                        // Story Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                h3.fw-bolder.mb-4 My Story
                                p After 20 years navigating between corporate environments and running my own company, I've witnessed firsthand the transformation that technology brings to business. But I've also seen the fear and confusion that often accompanies it.
                                p Many professionals today fall into two camps: those who are scared of AI and avoid it entirely, or those who blindly copy solutions without understanding why they work. Neither approach leads to sustainable success.
                                p.mb-0 That's why I don't just teach AI tools—I guide people on how to think about AI and how to best work alongside it. My mission is simple: turning "I don't know if this is for me" into "I know exactly how to use this."

                        // What I Do Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                h3.fw-bolder.mb-4 What I Do
                                p.mb-4 I'm currently building an HRTech startup and delivering AI training through multiple channels:
                                
                                .row.row-cols-1.row-cols-md-2.g-4.mb-4
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-start.bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                                i.bi.bi-camera-video
                                            div
                                                h5.fw-bold.mb-2 Webinars & Courses
                                                p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Interactive training sessions and comprehensive Udemy courses for professionals at all levels
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-start.bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                                i.bi.bi-briefcase
                                            div
                                                h5.fw-bold.mb-2 Business Consulting
                                                p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Direct consulting with businesses to implement AI strategies that actually work
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-start.bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                                i.bi.bi-rocket
                                            div
                                                h5.fw-bold.mb-2 HRTech Innovation
                                                p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Building cutting-edge solutions for modern human resources challenges
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-start.bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                                i.bi.bi-people
                                            div
                                                h5.fw-bold.mb-2 Strategic Training
                                                p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Teaching teams not just what to do, but how to think about AI integration

                        // Expertise Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                .d-flex.align-items-center.mb-4
                                    .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                        i.bi.bi-star-fill
                                    h3.fw-bolder.mb-0 Core Expertise
                                
                                .row.row-cols-1.row-cols-md-3.g-3
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-center.bg-light.rounded-4.p-3.h-100
                                            span AI Training & Education
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-center.bg-light.rounded-4.p-3.h-100
                                            span HRTech Solutions
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-center.bg-light.rounded-4.p-3.h-100
                                            span Business Strategy
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-center.bg-light.rounded-4.p-3.h-100
                                            span Corporate Innovation
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-center.bg-light.rounded-4.p-3.h-100
                                            span Change Management
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-center.bg-light.rounded-4.p-3.h-100
                                            span Digital Transformation

                        // Connect Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5.text-center
                                h3.fw-bolder.mb-4 Let's Connect
                                p.lead.mb-4 Interested in working together or learning more?
